source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_00<tab>The Allagan life support node's status light is blinking an ominous red...

TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_01<tab>The Allagan life support node informs you that atmospheric levels of corpse flower spores are at critically dangerous levels─and rising. Destroy corpse flowers to reduce the release of these apparently dangerous pollutants.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_01<tab>Das Lebenserhaltungssystem meldet eine besorgniserregende Konzentration von Sporen in der Luft. Besiege vier <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20DD6030502 /var> im Beta-Quadranten von Azys Lla.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_02<tab>You extirpate the troublesome corpse flowers. Return to the life support node to confirm that there are no other sources of dangerous atmospheric contaminants.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast die Luftverpester besiegt. Melde dem Lebenserhaltungssystem deinen Erfolg.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_03<tab>With the reduced rate of spore output, the life support system is now able to purify the air faster than it is being polluted. The abnormally high corpse flower population seems to have been caused by an airborne growth stimulation medium released from the ecological synthesis research facility.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_03<tab>Mit der verringerten Sporenbelastung ist das Lebenserhaltungssystem nicht mehr überfordert. Die Ursache für die abnormale Verbreitung <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 03F20DD6030302 /var> war wohl ein gasförmiges Wachstumsmittel, dass aus dem Rekombinationslabor entwichen ist.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_TODO_01<tab>Report to the life support node.

TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_000<tab>Atmospheric impurities at critical levels. Atmospheric corpse flower spore levels currently at one thousand three hundred and twelve percent of maximum safe limit and rising.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_000<tab><biep> Konzentration von Sporen in der Luft erreicht kritisches Niveau ... <biep> ... Verursacht von <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F20DD6030402 /var> ... <biep>

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_001<tab>Immediate destruction of corpse flowers is highly recommended to ensure citizen safety.
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_010<tab>Immediate destruction of corpse flowers is highly recommended to ensure continued citizen safety.
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_020<tab>Atmospheric corpse flower spore levels currently at one thousand three hundred and eleven percent of maximum safe limit and falling.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_020<tab><biep> <biep> Eliminierung <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 03F20DD6030302 /var> bestätigt. Sporenbelastung sinkt auf akzeptables Niveau.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_021<tab>Increased corpse flower population determined to be a result of atmospheric growth stimulation catalyst being unintentionally released by the ecological synthesis research facility. Transmitting report to research facility... <blip> <blip> Transmission complete.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_021<tab>Analyse hat ergeben ... abnormale Verbreitung <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 03F20DD6030302 /var> wurde verursacht durch gasförmiges Wachstumsmittel ... <biep> ... aus Rekombinationslabor entwichen ... <biep> Übertrage Bericht an Rekombinationslabor ...
